##################### Ansible Glaxay ##########################################


how to create new apache roles in ansible , 
# ansible-galaxy init common
#ansible-galaxy init apache

This command automatically create files inside the directory. 

tree  apache/
apache/
├── defaults
│   └── main.yml
├── handlers
│   └── main.yml
├── meta
│   └── main.yml
├── README.md
├── tasks
│   └── main.yml
├── tests
│   ├── inventory
│   └── test.yml
└── vars
    └── main.yml



